IO-AIO-Util
===========

This module provides useful functions missing from IO::AIO.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    File::Spec
    IO::AIO
    POSIX
    Test::More

